---
title: BeaconLink Authentication Flow
---

flowchart TB

    %% =====================================================
    %% Authentication Sources
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Clients["Authentication Clients"]

        User["Human Operator"]
        CLI["BeaconLink CLI"]
        Service["Platform Service"]
        Agent["BeaconLink Agent"]
        API["External API"]

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Entry Point
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Gateway["Access Layer"]

        APIGateway["API Gateway"]
        RateLimit["Rate Limiting"]
        RequestValidation["Request Validation"]

    end

    User --> APIGateway
    CLI --> APIGateway
    Service --> APIGateway
    Agent --> APIGateway
    API --> APIGateway

    APIGateway --> RateLimit
    RateLimit --> RequestValidation

    %% =====================================================
    %% Identity Verification
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Identity["Identity Verification"]

        IdP["Identity Provider"]

        MFA["Multi-Factor Authentication"]

        MTLS["Mutual TLS"]

        OIDC["OIDC / OAuth2"]

        Certificate["Certificate Validation"]

    end

    RequestValidation --> IdP

    IdP --> MFA
    IdP --> OIDC
    IdP --> MTLS

    MTLS --> Certificate

    %% =====================================================
    %% Credential Validation
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Credentials["Credential Validation"]

        Verify["Verify Credentials"]

        Expiration["Expiration Check"]

        Revocation["Revocation Check"]

        Trust["Trust Evaluation"]

    end

    MFA --> Verify
    OIDC --> Verify
    Certificate --> Verify

    Verify --> Expiration
    Expiration --> Revocation
    Revocation --> Trust

    %% =====================================================
    %% Authorization
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Authorization["Authorization Pipeline"]

        IdentityContext["Build Identity Context"]

        RBAC["Role-Based Access"]

        ABAC["Attribute-Based Access"]

        Policy["Policy Engine"]

        Decision{"Access Allowed?"}

    end

    Trust --> IdentityContext

    IdentityContext --> RBAC
    IdentityContext --> ABAC

    RBAC --> Policy
    ABAC --> Policy

    Policy --> Decision

    %% =====================================================
    %% Session Management
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Session["Secure Session"]

        Token["Issue Short-Lived Token"]

        SessionID["Create Session"]

        Audit["Audit Authentication"]

        Event["Security Event"]

    end

    Decision -->|Yes| Token

    Token --> SessionID
    SessionID --> Audit
    Audit --> Event

    %% =====================================================
    %% Resource Access
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Resources["Protected Platform Services"]

        Control["Control Plane"]

        Workflow["Workflow Engine"]

        Scheduler["Distributed Scheduler"]

        Secrets["Secret Management"]

        Relay["Relay Network"]

        Inventory["Inventory Service"]

    end

    SessionID --> Control
    SessionID --> Workflow
    SessionID --> Scheduler
    SessionID --> Secrets
    SessionID --> Relay
    SessionID --> Inventory

    %% =====================================================
    %% Authentication Failure
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Failure["Authentication Failure"]

        Reject["Reject Request"]

        Log["Security Audit Log"]

        Alert["Security Alert"]

        Lock["Temporary Lockout"]

    end

    Decision -->|No| Reject

    Reject --> Log
    Log --> Alert
    Alert --> Lock

    %% =====================================================
    %% Continuous Validation
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Continuous["Continuous Session Validation"]

        Heartbeat["Heartbeat"]

        TokenCheck["Token Validation"]

        PolicyCheck["Policy Re-Evaluation"]

        Renewal["Credential Renewal"]

    end

    SessionID --> Heartbeat

    Heartbeat --> TokenCheck
    TokenCheck --> PolicyCheck
    PolicyCheck --> Renewal

    Renewal --> Trust

    %% =====================================================
    %% Authentication Methods
    %% =====================================================

    Methods["Supported Authentication

• OIDC
• OAuth 2.0
• SAML
• LDAP
• Mutual TLS
• X.509 Certificates
• Service Accounts
• API Tokens
• Platform Identity"]

    Methods -.-> Identity

    %% =====================================================
    %% Security Principles
    %% =====================================================

    Principles["Authentication Principles

• Verify Every Request
• Identity Before Access
• Mutual TLS for Services
• Short-Lived Credentials
• Continuous Verification
• Policy-Driven Authorization
• Complete Audit Trail
• Zero Trust by Default"]

    Principles -.-> Credentials
    Principles -.-> Authorization
    Principles -.-> Continuous

